# ------------------------------------------
# 8.3 批量记录热度（为热榜填充数据）
# ------------------------------------------
### 批量访问记录 - 兵马俑（多次调用填充热度）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/rank/visit?attractionId=1001&userId=user001

###

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/rank/visit?attractionId=1001&userId=user002

###

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/rank/visit?attractionId=1006&userId=user001

###

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/rank/visit?attractionId=1006&userId=user003

###

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/rank/visit?attractionId=1013&userId=user002

###

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/rank/visit?attractionId=1010&userId=user004

###

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/rank/visit?attractionId=1014&userId=user005

###

### 填充热度后查看热榜
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rank/hot?topN=10

